description: Just under 1,000 doses are due to be delivered to the most high-risk islanders next week.
title: Covid: Pfizer/BioNTech vaccine arrives in Jersey
title_page: Covid: Pfizer/BioNTech vaccine arrives in Jersey - BBC News
maintext: The initial batch of just under 1,000 doses will be given to care home residents as a first priority, the government said.
